measurements.description: Forty-one flowers on three up to 71-cm arched inflorescences; sepals and petals chartreuse. maroon veins, blushed maroon except margins, dorsal sepal hooded, lateral sepals swept forward; lip fimbriate, cream spotted mahogany, keels ciliate, cream spotted mahogany; column light yellow, inferior surface spotted mahogany; substance firm; texture matte.
